title.newValue: Microsoft Teams: Excel Live for GCCH and DoD

description.oldValue:
Collaborate easily in Teams with our new Excel Live feature. With this feature, you can easily collaborate with all meeting participants on your Excel worksheet during the meeting. Select the file you want to share, grant permissions to meeting participants, and enable all meeting participants to edit the document from the meeting window.
GA date: April CY2023
